run our api from cmd

# Properties
-Xmx2048m   =2048m is the size of the given of disk
-Dspring.profiles.active=pdn    = production ambient
-Dserver.port= 88    = change the port

# Don't forget change the version of our api when finished sometime in build.gradle #
# go to the elephant of gradle -> tasks -> build -> bootJar and wait

# Commands
in the folder of our project
P:\Text JAVA\spring\platzi-market>java -jar build/libs/platzi-market-1.0.jar

if we want change from user dev to pdn:
java -jar -Dspring.profiles.active=pdn build/libs/platzi-market-1.0.jar